  "description": "A New Kinda Science Society",
  "body_html": "<p>Are you interested in trying to test physical laws at home? Maybe you like chemistry but don't want to be in academia? Or you like looking at stuff through your microscope after a hard day's work? And maybe want to try and do some rigorous science at home?</p><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!VYaF!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc41cda4c-6d38-4d3b-ab45-1e55120102a5_359x424.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!VYaF!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc41cda4c-6d38-4d3b-ab45-1e55120102a5_359x424.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!VYaF!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc41cda4c-6d38-4d3b-ab45-1e55120102a5_359x424.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!VYaF!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc41cda4c-6d38-4d3b-ab45-1e55120102a5_359x424.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!VYaF!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc41cda4c-6d38-4d3b-ab45-1e55120102a5_359x424.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!VYaF!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc41cda4c-6d38-4d3b-ab45-1e55120102a5_359x424.png\" width=\"728\" height=\"409.5\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/c41cda4c-6d38-4d3b-ab45-1e55120102a5_359x424.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:false,&quot;imageSize&quot;:&quot;normal&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:819,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:728,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;captionedImage&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" class=\"sizing-normal\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!VYaF!,w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc41cda4c-6d38-4d3b-ab45-1e55120102a5_359x424.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!VYaF!,w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc41cda4c-6d38-4d3b-ab45-1e55120102a5_359x424.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!VYaF!,w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc41cda4c-6d38-4d3b-ab45-1e55120102a5_359x424.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!VYaF!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc41cda4c-6d38-4d3b-ab45-1e55120102a5_359x424.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><div class=\"image-link-expand\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\"><button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\"><svg role=\"img\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><g><title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path></g></svg></button><button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\"><polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg></button></div></div></div></a></figure></div><p>You should join the Independent Science Society! We are a group that tries to figure out how <strong>good science can be done at home</strong>. We were awarded a grant from <a href=\"https://aria.org.uk/insights/breaking-bread-over-breaking-science/\">The Advanced Research and Invention Agency</a> as part of their Innovator Circles Program. We meet in London quite often and discuss science in cafes or in seminars. You can <a href=\"https://www.independentscience.org/\">join here</a>, where there\u2019s also a discord link.</p><p>So what is this thang?</p><p>I made a <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lL5NXkwElMA\">Youtube video</a> last year on trying and failing to do science in my free time after my day job.</p><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Bkeu!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0fd7ca7c-df9d-48f1-8e7b-d1cdd79aeaf8_1431x963.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Bkeu!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0fd7ca7c-df9d-48f1-8e7b-d1cdd79aeaf8_1431x963.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Bkeu!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0fd7ca7c-df9d-48f1-8e7b-d1cdd79aeaf8_1431x963.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Bkeu!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0fd7ca7c-df9d-48f1-8e7b-d1cdd79aeaf8_1431x963.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Bkeu!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0fd7ca7c-df9d-48f1-8e7b-d1cdd79aeaf8_1431x963.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Bkeu!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0fd7ca7c-df9d-48f1-8e7b-d1cdd79aeaf8_1431x963.png\" width=\"728\" height=\"409.5\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/0fd7ca7c-df9d-48f1-8e7b-d1cdd79aeaf8_1431x963.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:false,&quot;imageSize&quot;:&quot;normal&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:819,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:728,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;captionedImage&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" class=\"sizing-normal\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Bkeu!,w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0fd7ca7c-df9d-48f1-8e7b-d1cdd79aeaf8_1431x963.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Bkeu!,w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0fd7ca7c-df9d-48f1-8e7b-d1cdd79aeaf8_1431x963.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Bkeu!,w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0fd7ca7c-df9d-48f1-8e7b-d1cdd79aeaf8_1431x963.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Bkeu!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0fd7ca7c-df9d-48f1-8e7b-d1cdd79aeaf8_1431x963.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"></picture><div class=\"image-link-expand\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\"><button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\"><svg role=\"img\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><g><title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path></g></svg></button><button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\"><polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg></button></div></div></div></a></figure></div><p>Then I wrote a <a href=\"https://chillphysicsenjoyer.substack.com/p/pursuing-physics-research-part-time?utm_source=publication-search\">long ass essay</a> on why doing part time research can give you an edge over academia. These got quite popular, so I made a Discord group for people doing this. And learnt that a lot of people wanna do this.</p><p>I then realised that a society could be made from this. Why?</p><p>I realised that a lot of good science was done by people who started doing it in their free time. Like <a href=\"https://chillphysicsenjoyer.substack.com/p/the-man-i-want-to-meet-the-most?utm_source=publication-search\">Alfred Loomis</a> who initially was a utilities financier that used his money to start a radiation laboratory. There seems to be something about stuff motivated by curiosity that causes good work.</p><p>Also, there is a lot of science out there being discovered. AI is making it a lot easier to do science, which is a good thing! But the problem is that we need to check it. And we don't have enough people and science funding. There are so many different regimes to check physics that maybe a society like this is a good way to try to fix that problem.</p><p>There are also people who want to do science, are good, and don't have an in. But now there are less barriers to entry because <strong>no one</strong> don't know what it really means to do science anymore, given our advances in artificial intelligence - we have machines that can think!</p><p>But the main reason I made this society is that... its just fun... people like thinking about stuff and testing stuff and sharing it.</p><p>OK so what do we work on? One thing is finding problems that independent scientists can do. This means working at energy levels that are accessible from the kitchen, and stuff you can observe with a camera or microscope. We think there are plenty of unanswered questions. How far does a sneeze travel? Can you observe brownian motion with a microscope and when will the conditions break down?</p><p>We also try to figure out how to automate stuff and be super cheap so we can try to rival bigger labs.</p><p>In terms of rigour and replicability, we discuss methods on being our best empirical selves. What does it mean to run a valid experiment? How can we use formal methods to check our own math?</p><p>So far we've done a bunch of events in London!</p><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!ty63!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff9098102-0c83-451a-9c71-5418b3389e91_628x988.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!ty63!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff9098102-0c83-451a-9c71-5418b3389e91_628x988.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!ty63!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff9098102-0c83-451a-9c71-5418b3389e91_628x988.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!ty63!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff9098102-0c83-451a-9c71-5418b3389e91_628x988.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!ty63!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_p